---
<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container footer-grid">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="Charizard Token Logo" class="footer-logo" />
        CHARIZARD <span class="text-gradient">TOKEN</span>
      </div>
      <p>The strategic evolution of meme-fi. Fast. Deflationary. Unstoppable.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer-links">
      <div class="link-group">
        <h4>Ecosystem</h4>
        <a href="#tokenomics">Tokenomics</a>
        <a href="#buy">Buy $CHZ</a>
        <a href="#utility">Utility</a>
      </div>
      <div class="link-group">
        <h4>Community</h4>
        <a href="https://t.me/+vQBILWIpJqQwOGI0" target="_blank">Telegram</a>
        <a href="https://x.com/Token_Charizard" target="_blank">Twitter / X</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2026 Charizard Token. Fan-made homage inspired by the legend of Charizard.</p>
      <p class="disclaimer">Always DYOR. Crypto assets carry risk.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    padding: 6rem 0 2rem;
    background: #050505;
  }

  .footer-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .footer-logo {
    height: 40px;
    width: auto;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-right: 0.75rem;
    object-fit: contain;
  }

  .footer-brand p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .footer-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .link-group h4 {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .link-group a {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .link-group a:hover {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .footer-bottom {
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .disclaimer {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .footer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem; }
    .footer-links { gap: 2rem; }
  }
</style>

